            There is, however, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one</NUMEX> big difference between <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">America</ENAMEX> then
and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Japan</ENAMEX> now. <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Japan</ENAMEX> can no longer use conventional monetary and fiscal
