<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">ignominiously</ENAMEX> fail.

            But if the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">BOJ</ENAMEX> is determined enough--and if people
like me have analyzed <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Japan</ENAMEX>'s plight correctly--then <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">six months</TIMEX> or a year from
now <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Japan</ENAMEX> may be on the road to an economic recovery more dramatic than anyone
